The chunk contains specific Client Agent control messages related to interest management, including commands to add or remove interests, which are crucial for managing what objects or zones the client is tracking.

CLIENTAGENT_CLEAR_POST_REMOVES =              1111
CLIENTAGENT_ADD_INTEREST =                    1200
CLIENTAGENT_ADD_INTEREST_MULTIPLE =           1201
CLIENTAGENT_REMOVE_INTEREST =                 1203
